CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On review of the notice of automatic exclusion filed by the Office of Attorney Services, it is evident that Cara McClellan has not complied with the pro hac vice registration requirements as outlined in Gov.Bar R. XII. Therefore, the pro hac vice admission of Cara McClellan is revoked.
